## å¿«é€Ÿå¼€å§‹

### åˆ›å»ºçª—å£

```python
from PyToolsgr import PyToolsgr

# è®¾ç½®æ“ä½œç³»ç»Ÿ
PyToolsgr.OS('Windows')

# çª—å£å‚æ•°
resolution = (1080, 720)  # çª—å£å¤§å°
fullscreen = False      # æ˜¯å¦å…¨å±
title = 'PyToolsgr'     # çª—å£æ ‡é¢˜
resizable = True        # æ˜¯å¦å¯ä»¥è°ƒæ•´çª—å£å¤§å°
fps_limit = 60          # æœ€å¤§å¸§ç‡
show_fps = True         # æ˜¯å¦æ˜¾ç¤ºå¸§ç‡
physics = True          # æ˜¯å¦å¼€å¯ç‰©ç†å¼•æ“
mode = '2d'             # 2dæˆ–3d

# åˆ›å»ºæ¸¸æˆçª—å£
game = PyToolsgr.game(
    resolution=resolution,
    fullscreen=fullscreen,
    title=title,
    resizable=resizable,
    fps_limit=fps_limit,
    show_fps=show_fps,
    physics=physics,
    mode=mode
)

# è¿è¡Œæ¸¸æˆ
game.run()
```

